= <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> Congress

A party congress has been called within the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> over proposed internal reform that would turn the party into a genuine <span style="color: #C0A054;">**People's Party**</span>, not one of industrial interests. 

German industry isn't going to abandon their voice within the <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> so easily, and this is likely to be the last chance Stresemann will have to maintain control of the party, with his declining health.[? if not in_grand_coalition: The left of our party has also been diminished by the current absence of a coalition including both parties. ?]

